      "title": "Star Lite Motel",
      "score": 0.09742540823936781,
      "text": "Star Lite Motel\nThe Star Lite Motel is a historic motel in Dilworth, Minnesota. It is one of the oldest buildings in Dilworth, and the oldest motel in Clay County. Earlier it was known as Charley's Motel. A previous owner created the neon sign that is regarded as the motel's most noteworthy feature.",
