      "title": "Walnut Grove, Washington",
      "score": 0.04496675245490682,
      "text": "Walnut Grove, Washington\nWalnut Grove is a census-designated place (CDP) in Clark County, Washington, United States. The population was 9,790 at the 2010 census, up from 7,164 at the 2000 census.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05312757357265758,
